<br>
<br>
Castersrealm suggest <br>
<br>
For mana focus:<br>
25 Intelligence and 5 Strength.<br>
<br>
And<br>
<br>
For HP Focus:<br>
add 25 Stamina, 5 Intelligence.<br>
<br>
But I really don't know wich one is the most important for a wiz =/<br>
<br>
Also the race is either going to be DE or HE but I haven't decided yet. Any tips will help, thank you! <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zertez>zertez</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 131<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/21/03 11:59 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re:Wich is more important, Mana focus Or HP focus?</span><hr size=1>  The sticky thread at the top is a great source of information. <br>
<br>
 <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://pub140.ezboard.com/fgraffeswizardcompilationfrm1.showMessage?topicID=25380.topic">pub140.ezboard.com/fgraff...5380.topic</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--> <p></p><i>Edited by: <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=zertez>zertez</A> at: 5/22/03 12:03:00 am<br></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=xoshia>Xoshia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Forum Wizard</span><br>  Posts: 62<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/22/03 12:00 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Wich is more important, Mana focus Or HP focus?</span><hr size=1> Id personally go Int.<br>
although it wont matter in the end game due to all items that high having like +15 to all ect for most players the int will make a difference.<br>
<br>
as a wiz your not meant to get hit and the hps from the points in sta would probably not give much , direct hp gear would be better imo<br>
<br>
the mana pool is important , could mean the difference in killing a mob or having to med when the target is like 5% <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=664016" target="top">Xoshia Zensolar</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> - Sorceress of 60th Cycles<br>
