<br>
Obviously, the higher level you get the easier this becomes to do (depending on your guild) as you gain access to items with large numbers of both hp and mana, etc. <p><A HREF="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=7124" TARGET="_blank">Sage Zealpath Skyphire</A><BR>
<A HREF="http://www.graffe.com">Arcanist</A> of <A HREF="http://www.valoran.org/">Valoran</A><BR>
