<br>
Dump points into int and put a few into stamina after that.  It'd be stupid to focus on stamina at the expense of int.  If you end up hitting the int cap ever, you can just wear more pure hp items. <p><center><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=61177">Gherad</a>            <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=72580">Peleg</a>
