<br>
Not true.  I wish I had put all my points in stamina and none  in int.  As it is, if I were not capped, my int would be somewhere around 450 unbuffed, higher with c5, and I'm not even in time yet.<br>
<br>
My stamina is not maxed at this point even with a stamina buff.<br>
<br>
I'd rather have mana than hp, but after the cap, int doesn't add mana.<br>
<br>
Like a lot of people have said, it all depends how far you are going to go.  If you see yourself in elemental + gear, then I'd put my points in stamina.  If you see yourself in a noob guild or a mid range guild, I'd probably go for int.<br>
